          <annotation class='point' id='2' mark-position='1' pullback='0' text-width='318'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#555555' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Persistent Debt Burden:</run>
              <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#555555' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> Lower borrowing costs have not yet triggered consumer deleveraging. Reliance on high-interest credit remains at historic highs.</run>
            </formatted-text>
