          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='4219' hidden='true' id='6' story-point-id='1' type-v2='text' w='29622' x='40852' y='26301'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Navigating the 2028 Financial Cliff</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='52883' id='11' story-point-id='5' type-v2='text' w='81994' x='8228' y='22504'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#666666' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Prioritize customers under 45:</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#666666' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> Focus debt consolidation and HELOC solutions on younger homeowners, who are carrying the highest debt burdens and are likely to face the greatest pressure as mortgages come up for renewal.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#666666' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Reallocate branch resources toward retention:</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#666666' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> Shift branch capacity and advisory efforts away from new mortgage originations and place greater emphasis on customer retention, financial planning, and debt restructuring to support existing clients through the renewal cycle.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#666666' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Expand automated micro-investing solutions:</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#666666' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> Introduce low-barrier investment features, such as round-up savings and recurring micro-investments, to help cash-constrained customers gradually build emergency savings and improve their long-term financial resilience.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{11DFC6A3-0FF7-491C-B4F6-C5F6CBE83529}' />
    </dashboard>
